1
00:01:40,180 --> 00:01:44,800
=Love Story in the 1970s=

2
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:47,940
=Episode 2=

3
00:01:50,871 --> 00:01:52,004
Fei Ni, you're back?

4
00:01:52,140 --> 00:01:52,660
Mr. Zhou.

5
00:01:52,660 --> 00:01:52,970
Yeah.

6
00:01:54,810 --> 00:01:55,580
Fei Ni!

7
00:01:57,580 --> 00:01:58,370
Lin Mei.

8
00:01:58,370 --> 00:01:59,620
(Lin Mei)

9
00:01:59,970 --> 00:02:00,370
Let's go.

10
00:02:02,060 --> 00:02:02,610
Look.

11
00:02:02,610 --> 00:02:03,450
What's this?

12
00:02:04,020 --> 00:02:05,220
No one visits a patient

13
00:02:05,220 --> 00:02:06,170
and brings things back

14
00:02:06,170 --> 00:02:07,330
from the hospital like you.

15
00:02:07,330 --> 00:02:08,450
He can't eat it, anyway,

16
00:02:08,450 --> 00:02:10,137
so I brought it back
to let you try it.

17
00:02:10,820 --> 00:02:11,730
It's delicious.

18
00:02:12,450 --> 00:02:13,730
Let me show you something.

19
00:02:14,650 --> 00:02:15,540
This.

20
00:02:16,490 --> 00:02:17,490
Look.

21
00:02:21,100 --> 00:02:22,050
It's so big.

22
00:02:22,050 --> 00:02:23,270
How did you get this?

23
00:02:23,270 --> 00:02:24,580
Stealing from the tiger's mouth.

24
00:02:25,420 --> 00:02:26,690
I took it from my house.

25
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:29,020
This won't do. Take it back.

26
00:02:29,020 --> 00:02:30,560
Or your brother
and your sister-in-law

27
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,210
will devour you.

28
00:02:31,210 --> 00:02:32,160
It's fine.

29
00:02:32,300 --> 00:02:33,350
I still have this.

30
00:02:34,050 --> 00:02:34,800
I'm telling you.

31
00:02:35,350 --> 00:02:37,820
I've been secretly gathering
half a jin of meat tickets

32
00:02:37,820 --> 00:02:39,950
and five jin of national grain tickets
in the last two months.

33
00:02:39,970 --> 00:02:42,050
Send these to your brother as well.

34
00:02:46,930 --> 00:02:47,690
You're so nice.

35
00:02:49,450 --> 00:02:50,140
All right.

36
00:02:50,700 --> 00:02:52,260
I'll go to the post office tomorrow.

37
00:02:52,260 --> 00:02:54,730
I'll send all of these to my brother,

38
00:02:56,210 --> 00:02:58,100
so it won't take him too long

39
00:02:58,140 --> 00:03:00,860
to get your gift full of love.

40
00:03:01,730 --> 00:03:03,540
He will never appreciate my effort.

41
00:03:04,730 --> 00:03:05,800
Did you two argue again?

42
00:03:07,890 --> 00:03:09,350
Enough talk about us.

43
00:03:10,730 --> 00:03:11,490
Let me ask you.

44
00:03:12,860 --> 00:03:13,820
Well...

45
00:03:14,330 --> 00:03:15,210
That...

46
00:03:15,820 --> 00:03:16,730
Yang...

47
00:03:16,730 --> 00:03:17,650
Fang Muyang.

48
00:03:18,170 --> 00:03:19,380
His name doesn't matter.

49
00:03:20,020 --> 00:03:22,470
Anyway, can you really attend university

50
00:03:22,730 --> 00:03:24,190
if he wakes up?

51
00:03:28,140 --> 00:03:29,810
It's not guaranteed,

52
00:03:30,100 --> 00:03:32,840
but there's a 90% chance, at least.

53
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,350
As long as he can wake up,

54
00:03:34,580 --> 00:03:36,271
I'll be a winner
for the rest of my life.

55
00:03:36,580 --> 00:03:37,980
What if he doesn't wake up?

56
00:03:38,930 --> 00:03:41,330
Knock on wood!

57
00:03:41,330 --> 00:03:41,890
Touch wood.

58
00:03:42,100 --> 00:03:43,380
- Touch wood.
- Touch wood.

59
00:03:43,380 --> 00:03:44,930
He will surely wake up. Say it.

60
00:03:44,930 --> 00:03:45,930
Say it.

61
00:03:45,930 --> 00:03:47,100
He will surely wake up.

62
00:03:47,100 --> 00:03:47,890
He must wake up.

63
00:03:47,890 --> 00:03:48,210
Yes.

64
00:03:48,210 --> 00:03:50,619
If he dares to stay asleep,
I'll pinch him until he wakes up.

65
00:03:50,620 --> 00:03:51,210
Pinch him here.

66
00:03:51,293 --> 00:03:52,470
Stop!

67
00:03:53,982 --> 00:03:55,880
Tomorrow, both of us
will go and pinch him.

68
00:03:55,880 --> 00:03:56,330
No!

69
00:03:56,330 --> 00:03:57,150
Pinch it here.

70
00:03:57,340 --> 00:03:59,650
- We'll pinch him here at the hospital.
- No!

71
00:04:02,020 --> 00:04:02,770
Seriously,

72
00:04:03,050 --> 00:04:05,030
if that hero really does wake up,

73
00:04:05,450 --> 00:04:06,950
you get to attend university,

74
00:04:07,350 --> 00:04:09,270
and your brother comes back
and we get married,

75
00:04:09,537 --> 00:04:11,440
isn't that three auspicious events
all at once?

76
00:04:15,490 --> 00:04:16,760
That day will come.

77
00:04:21,700 --> 00:04:23,780
(Jiangcheng Worker-Peasant Hospital)

78
00:04:33,020 --> 00:04:39,060
♪If the future cannot be touched♪

79
00:04:39,820 --> 00:04:43,060
♪Don't think too far ahead♪

80
00:04:43,060 --> 00:04:46,460
♪Just work hard for today♪

81
00:04:46,820 --> 00:04:50,100
♪Learn from the sun, how warm it is♪

82
00:04:50,770 --> 00:04:51,900
(The head nurse told me)

83
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:53,960
(massaging improves your chances
of waking up.)

84
00:04:54,060 --> 00:04:55,770
(You must wake up quickly.)

85
00:04:57,020 --> 00:04:59,300
♪Will receive the most♪

86
00:05:00,540 --> 00:05:03,940
♪Live it real♪

87
00:05:04,020 --> 00:05:07,380
♪A down-to-earth life♪

88
00:05:07,700 --> 00:05:10,860
♪Slowly getting along with you♪

89
00:05:10,970 --> 00:05:12,180
Call me if the drip finishes.

90
00:05:14,540 --> 00:05:17,780
♪Live it real♪

91
00:05:17,860 --> 00:05:21,180
♪Two people, three meals, four seasons♪

92
00:05:21,540 --> 00:05:24,740
♪Collecting ordinary moments in life♪

93
00:05:24,820 --> 00:05:27,100
♪Making them into memories♪

94
00:05:42,260 --> 00:05:45,740
♪Live it real♪

95
00:05:45,780 --> 00:05:49,180
♪A down-to-earth life♪

96
00:05:49,540 --> 00:05:52,460
♪The cloudy days and rain along the way♪

97
00:05:52,460 --> 00:05:53,490
(Fei Ni...)

98
00:05:53,730 --> 00:05:55,620
(Think of this as a trial for you.)

99
00:05:56,140 --> 00:05:57,770
(Attending university is not easy.)

100
00:05:58,140 --> 00:05:59,020
Head Nurse!

101
00:05:59,420 --> 00:06:02,980
♪Two people, three meals, four seasons♪

102
00:06:03,060 --> 00:06:06,100
♪Collecting sweet moments in life♪

103
00:06:06,260 --> 00:06:08,540
♪Making them into memories♪

104
00:06:28,940 --> 00:06:31,060
Sorry. That wasn't on purpose.

105
00:06:43,260 --> 00:06:44,770
Seriously, this...

106
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:47,580
Why did your skin become fair
after lying here for a month?

107
00:06:55,426 --> 00:06:57,382
When I pretended to sleep
when I was young,

108
00:06:57,850 --> 00:06:59,770
my brother would pull my eyelashes.

109
00:07:04,210 --> 00:07:05,090
Fang Muyang,

110
00:07:06,260 --> 00:07:08,210
I wish you were
just pretending to sleep.

111
00:07:15,300 --> 00:07:18,580
(Jiangcheng No. 1 Textile Factory)

112
00:07:21,740 --> 00:07:22,330
How is it?

113
00:07:22,660 --> 00:07:23,530
Did anyone suspect us

114
00:07:23,530 --> 00:07:24,720
of what happened that day?

115
00:07:24,940 --> 00:07:26,960
I probed Ms. Liu thoroughly.

116
00:07:27,210 --> 00:07:28,530
It was chaotic that day.

117
00:07:28,530 --> 00:07:29,826
I don't think anyone noticed you.

118
00:07:30,060 --> 00:07:31,620
Moreover, it has been so long.

119
00:07:32,020 --> 00:07:32,850
Don't worry.

120
00:07:35,180 --> 00:07:36,140
I'm not afraid.

121
00:07:36,493 --> 00:07:38,204
We are officially in a relationship.

122
00:07:38,493 --> 00:07:40,020
We will get married sooner or later.

123
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:44,648
We are not married as long as we
still haven't obtained the certificate.

124
00:07:44,770 --> 00:07:46,620
If they see us sleeping together,

125
00:07:46,620 --> 00:07:48,090
it'll be an ethical offense.

126
00:07:48,090 --> 00:07:49,804
It'll be all over for us! Do you get it?

127
00:07:49,890 --> 00:07:50,740
I get it.

128
00:07:52,290 --> 00:07:54,540
In the end, it was because
your parents looked down on me

129
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:55,740
for being a normal factory worker

130
00:07:55,740 --> 00:07:57,910
who was not a good match
for a university graduate like you.

131
00:07:57,915 --> 00:08:00,410
If we get married, there's
no need for us to act sneakily.

132
00:08:01,140 --> 00:08:02,530
So, before we get married,

133
00:08:02,530 --> 00:08:05,871
you must get the quota from the factory
to recommend you to attend university.

134
00:08:09,500 --> 00:08:10,770
I'm not that capable.

135
00:08:11,850 --> 00:08:12,940
I still need to rely on you.

136
00:08:14,090 --> 00:08:15,260
Of course, I will help you.

137
00:08:16,260 --> 00:08:17,740
However, it's troublesome

138
00:08:17,782 --> 00:08:19,915
because the factory
only has one spot available.

139
00:08:20,137 --> 00:08:21,520
Fei Ni is also fighting for it.

140
00:08:22,310 --> 00:08:23,230
What should we do?

141
00:08:23,530 --> 00:08:24,330
In the end,

142
00:08:24,330 --> 00:08:26,180
I'm just not as qualified as Fei Ni.

143
00:08:26,620 --> 00:08:28,290
Why are you such a good-for-nothing?

144
00:08:30,090 --> 00:08:31,410
How are you worse than her?

145
00:08:31,530 --> 00:08:33,620
I'm sick of seeing
how self-righteous she is.

146
00:08:33,620 --> 00:08:35,040
She studies more than you, so what?

147
00:08:35,860 --> 00:08:36,740
"Clarity"?

148
00:08:37,100 --> 00:08:38,520
She just wants to embarrass me.

149
00:08:39,530 --> 00:08:40,520
Fang Muyang, too.

150
00:08:41,100 --> 00:08:42,250
If he wakes up

151
00:08:43,020 --> 00:08:44,050
and exposes us,

152
00:08:44,050 --> 00:08:45,260
we'll be doomed.

153
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:47,140
No.

154
00:08:47,740 --> 00:08:48,890
I must think of something

155
00:08:48,890 --> 00:08:49,709
and make the factory

156
00:08:49,710 --> 00:08:51,910
decide who gets the university spot
as soon as possible.

157
00:08:52,050 --> 00:08:53,570
When everything has been decided,

158
00:08:53,860 --> 00:08:55,020
we'll be safe.

159
00:08:59,060 --> 00:09:05,300
(Jiangcheng Worker-Peasant Hospital)

160
00:09:05,460 --> 00:09:08,620
The head nurse asks me
to talk to you more.

161
00:09:08,620 --> 00:09:11,220
If you can hear me, you will hear me.

162
00:09:11,410 --> 00:09:13,782
If you can't, just think of it
as I'm talking to myself.

163
00:09:14,410 --> 00:09:16,440
The weather has become hot recently.

164
00:09:17,260 --> 00:09:18,690
I've changed your blanket for you.

165
00:09:19,260 --> 00:09:21,710
If you feel cold, just let me know.

166
00:09:25,620 --> 00:09:26,930
You can't tell me anyway.

167
00:09:27,890 --> 00:09:29,770
But I think you won't feel cold.

168
00:10:01,530 --> 00:10:02,410
Fang Muyang,

169
00:10:03,050 --> 00:10:04,210
did you draw this?

170
00:10:04,690 --> 00:10:06,220
You draw well.

171
00:10:11,170 --> 00:10:13,020
This is the Great Northern Wilderness.

172
00:10:16,410 --> 00:10:17,260
It's so pretty.

173
00:10:34,050 --> 00:10:35,410
There's so much money.

174
00:10:40,380 --> 00:10:41,170
Fang Muyang,

175
00:10:41,170 --> 00:10:43,410
do you remember
that you still owe me money?

176
00:10:46,182 --> 00:10:48,848
When you wake up,
I'll settle the score with you.

177
00:11:00,020 --> 00:11:06,340
(Inpatient Department)

178
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:14,720
I finally found you.

179
00:11:15,100 --> 00:11:15,770
What is it?

180
00:11:15,770 --> 00:11:16,930
Is Fang Muyang awake?

181
00:11:16,930 --> 00:11:19,260
(Nurse Zhou)
No. Fang Muyang's family is here.

182
00:11:19,380 --> 00:11:20,380
Who?

183
00:11:20,380 --> 00:11:21,620
His girlfriend.

184
00:11:22,140 --> 00:11:23,380
His girlfriend?

185
00:11:24,170 --> 00:11:24,690
I've...

186
00:11:34,510 --> 00:11:35,100
Hello.

187
00:11:39,170 --> 00:11:41,170
(Ling Yi)
Hello, I am Ling Yi.

188
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:43,137
- I'm Fang Muyang's...
- I know.

189
00:11:43,690 --> 00:11:45,140
You are Fang Muyang's girlfriend.

190
00:11:55,220 --> 00:11:58,580
(Office)

191
00:12:02,890 --> 00:12:03,460
Fei Ni,

192
00:12:03,460 --> 00:12:04,770
where's Fang Muyang's girlfriend?

193
00:12:04,804 --> 00:12:06,804
She's discussing his condition
with Dr. Liang.

194
00:12:10,620 --> 00:12:11,730
Listen to me, then.

195
00:12:11,730 --> 00:12:13,040
Since his girlfriend is here,

196
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:14,290
send him away immediately.

197
00:12:15,460 --> 00:12:16,426
You don't understand?

198
00:12:16,930 --> 00:12:17,860
I'm only telling you

199
00:12:17,860 --> 00:12:18,860
all these things

200
00:12:18,860 --> 00:12:19,740
because you've been

201
00:12:19,930 --> 00:12:21,410
taking care of him all these days

202
00:12:21,410 --> 00:12:22,650
without slacking.

203
00:12:24,140 --> 00:12:26,140
A patient like Fang Muyang

204
00:12:26,140 --> 00:12:28,260
will usually sleep for a few years

205
00:12:28,500 --> 00:12:30,380
or even a few decades.

206
00:12:30,770 --> 00:12:32,382
In the past, the factory sent you here

207
00:12:32,404 --> 00:12:35,050
because he had no relatives
or friends to take care of him.

208
00:12:35,260 --> 00:12:37,220
Now that his girlfriend is here,

209
00:12:37,220 --> 00:12:38,690
you should send him away.

210
00:12:43,071 --> 00:12:44,850
You're already tired
from taking care of him.

211
00:12:49,460 --> 00:12:50,530
(This is bad.)

212
00:12:50,800 --> 00:12:52,760
(If Fang Muyang
doesn't need me anymore,)

213
00:12:53,570 --> 00:12:55,150
(what will happen to my quota?)

214
00:12:55,880 --> 00:12:57,140
(What about my university?)

215
00:13:05,100 --> 00:13:05,770
Fei Ni,

216
00:13:08,260 --> 00:13:09,460
can I have a talk with you?

217
00:13:23,071 --> 00:13:25,590
I only found out he was injured
after reading the newspaper.

218
00:13:26,218 --> 00:13:27,188
I didn't expect him

219
00:13:28,137 --> 00:13:29,471
to be so seriously injured.

220
00:13:30,570 --> 00:13:32,510
Fang Muyang is a lot better now.

221
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:33,930
Waking up

222
00:13:34,410 --> 00:13:35,690
is just a matter of time.

223
00:13:41,930 --> 00:13:44,170
Are you from the same school
as Fang Muyang?

224
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,530
We were classmates for a year

225
00:13:46,530 --> 00:13:47,890
in middle school.

226
00:13:49,500 --> 00:13:50,740
No wonder you look familiar.

227
00:13:53,460 --> 00:13:54,610
I heard the head nurse say

228
00:13:54,610 --> 00:13:56,500
you've been the one
taking care of Fang Muyang.

229
00:13:56,760 --> 00:13:58,350
I thank you on behalf of Fang Muyang.

230
00:14:00,650 --> 00:14:03,220
(Is she going to shake my hand
and take over the duties from me?)

231
00:14:12,620 --> 00:14:13,280
You're welcome.

232
00:14:15,650 --> 00:14:16,410
You...

233
00:14:19,690 --> 00:14:21,140
(Don't say it.)

234
00:14:21,650 --> 00:14:23,740
(Don't say that you no longer need me.)

235
00:14:25,570 --> 00:14:26,570
(Don't say it...)

236
00:14:27,382 --> 00:14:29,204
How long can you take care of him?

237
00:14:32,460 --> 00:14:33,460
Can I ask you to help me

238
00:14:33,460 --> 00:14:34,810
take care of him for a while?

239
00:14:35,220 --> 00:14:36,860
Since you were his classmates.

240
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:40,182
No problem. I can take care of him
for as long as you need.

241
00:14:40,182 --> 00:14:40,782
No.

242
00:14:41,770 --> 00:14:42,770
I mean...

243
00:14:43,260 --> 00:14:44,460
Fang Muyang is injured

244
00:14:44,460 --> 00:14:46,248
because he saved our factory's worker.

245
00:14:46,248 --> 00:14:49,170
So, it's only right for me to take
care of him on behalf of the factory.

246
00:14:50,860 --> 00:14:51,570
That's great.

247
00:14:53,740 --> 00:14:55,780
I'll be leaving after I get my luggage.

248
00:14:56,100 --> 00:14:57,700
You're already leaving?

249
00:14:58,260 --> 00:15:00,020
I just came back
from an interview abroad.

250
00:15:00,020 --> 00:15:02,170
I still need to write up an article
after I return to university.

251
00:15:02,182 --> 00:15:03,782
I'll come and visit him when I'm free.

252
00:15:05,020 --> 00:15:05,980
University?

253
00:15:06,500 --> 00:15:07,060
Are you

254
00:15:07,140 --> 00:15:08,610
enrolled in a university?

255
00:15:10,650 --> 00:15:11,880
The production team had a spot

256
00:15:11,880 --> 00:15:13,380
to enroll in the university last year.

257
00:15:13,740 --> 00:15:14,220
They...

258
00:15:14,930 --> 00:15:16,340
They gave me the spot.

259
00:15:18,980 --> 00:15:19,650
Congratulations.

260
00:15:33,770 --> 00:15:34,570
Fei Ni,

261
00:15:34,570 --> 00:15:35,620
what's going on?

262
00:15:35,620 --> 00:15:37,937
Why did his girlfriend
leave with all her luggage?

263
00:15:38,460 --> 00:15:41,530
She said she'd be back in a few days.

264
00:15:42,537 --> 00:15:44,650
It seems like
you'll be stuck here for a while.

265
00:15:45,930 --> 00:15:48,890
Zhou, do you have any other method

266
00:15:49,340 --> 00:15:51,170
to let him wake up sooner?

267
00:15:51,460 --> 00:15:53,530
I have no idea.

268
00:15:54,100 --> 00:15:56,340
Didn't the head nurse ask you

269
00:15:56,340 --> 00:15:57,620
to chat more with him

270
00:15:59,170 --> 00:15:59,980
or let him

271
00:15:59,980 --> 00:16:01,937
listen to some music
that he liked in the past?

272
00:16:02,170 --> 00:16:03,140
Music?

273
00:16:03,530 --> 00:16:04,690
It might be useful.

274
00:16:04,782 --> 00:16:06,100
What about revolutionary operas?

275
00:16:06,604 --> 00:16:08,004
As long as it has a tune.

276
00:16:30,980 --> 00:16:32,200
This is your father's treasure.

277
00:16:33,271 --> 00:16:35,170
It's difficult
to find this second-hand radio.

278
00:16:35,170 --> 00:16:36,080
Don't spoil it.

279
00:16:36,570 --> 00:16:37,710
Don't worry, Mom.

280
00:16:37,893 --> 00:16:39,604
It'll be around
as long as I'm still alive.

281
00:16:40,826 --> 00:16:42,160
You go to work at night

282
00:16:42,182 --> 00:16:44,226
and still need to go to the hospital
during the day.

283
00:16:44,226 --> 00:16:45,290
Can't you take a break?

284
00:16:45,650 --> 00:16:47,050
Do you think you're made from steel?

285
00:16:47,050 --> 00:16:48,650
We'll change shifts tomorrow.

286
00:16:48,650 --> 00:16:50,410
They want this batch of goods urgently.

287
00:16:50,410 --> 00:16:51,460
We need to rush it.

288
00:16:51,460 --> 00:16:52,620
If the delivery is delayed,

289
00:16:52,620 --> 00:16:54,026
we'll have to pay a compensation.

290
00:16:55,620 --> 00:16:57,290
We still have food on the table.

291
00:16:57,740 --> 00:16:59,620
Do you think you have too much money?

292
00:17:01,740 --> 00:17:03,740
Liu, who lives downstairs,

293
00:17:04,020 --> 00:17:05,850
is also kind-hearted. She thinks

294
00:17:06,090 --> 00:17:07,570
my daughter is very pretty

295
00:17:07,570 --> 00:17:08,610
and needs a partner.

296
00:17:08,610 --> 00:17:09,315
Coincidentally,

297
00:17:09,320 --> 00:17:11,570
- the clothing factory has a man...
- Mom, I don't want a partner.

298
00:17:11,570 --> 00:17:13,090
Just leave me alone.

299
00:17:13,940 --> 00:17:15,980
Having money is the most important.

300
00:17:17,570 --> 00:17:19,460
Fine. Don't sleep too late.

301
00:17:27,090 --> 00:17:30,290
Fang Muyang, this is enough.

302
00:17:30,570 --> 00:17:32,420
You've been lying here
for more than a month.

303
00:17:32,420 --> 00:17:34,493
If you don't wake up,
I'll stop taking care of you.

304
00:17:37,900 --> 00:17:40,110
I really owe you in my previous life.

305
00:17:41,260 --> 00:17:44,050
I'm not trying to scare you.

306
00:17:44,260 --> 00:17:45,420
If you don't wake up,

307
00:17:45,420 --> 00:17:46,850
you'll even lose your girlfriend.

308
00:17:47,330 --> 00:17:49,260
She hasn't been here
since her last visit.

309
00:17:51,660 --> 00:17:53,940
I'm not trying to sow discord

310
00:17:53,940 --> 00:17:55,050
but I just want to say

311
00:17:55,050 --> 00:17:57,293
that it'll be good for both of us
if you wake up sooner.

312
00:18:09,900 --> 00:18:11,460
You listen to this play the whole day.

313
00:18:11,460 --> 00:18:13,570
My ears are going to burst from this.

314
00:18:13,900 --> 00:18:15,900
Any more and I will
be able to do the play myself.

315
00:18:29,020 --> 00:18:30,700
It's out of battery.

316
00:18:55,130 --> 00:18:56,370
You force me to do this.

317
00:19:13,900 --> 00:19:15,570
This is your book.

318
00:19:16,260 --> 00:19:17,660
I didn't want to do this

319
00:19:17,660 --> 00:19:18,940
because it was too dangerous.

320
00:19:18,940 --> 00:19:20,130
Right now,

321
00:19:20,330 --> 00:19:22,130
I have no other choice.

322
00:19:22,130 --> 00:19:23,740
I'll read a few pages for you.

323
00:19:23,900 --> 00:19:26,460
However, you mustn't report me
when you wake up.

324
00:19:26,460 --> 00:19:27,982
Otherwise, my role model will be gone.

325
00:19:39,610 --> 00:19:44,530
We hope beautiful lives
can keep spreading.

326
00:19:44,740 --> 00:19:45,460
That is how

327
00:19:46,290 --> 00:19:49,230
the beautiful roses will forever exist.

328
00:19:49,660 --> 00:19:51,360
If mature things

329
00:19:51,670 --> 00:19:53,360
must cease to exist in the world,

330
00:19:53,940 --> 00:19:57,700
the beautiful descendants will
continue to spread fragrance.

331
00:20:09,500 --> 00:20:13,680
However, you are engaged
with the sparkling eyes of yours.

332
00:20:14,960 --> 00:20:17,760
Fei Ni, it's me. Open the door.

333
00:20:18,700 --> 00:20:20,180
Coming.

334
00:20:26,330 --> 00:20:27,460
Are you wiping him down?

335
00:20:28,004 --> 00:20:29,420
It's time to take your temperature.

336
00:20:36,804 --> 00:20:39,560
Why don't you take his temperature
after you finish wiping him down?

337
00:20:40,810 --> 00:20:41,700
Sure.

338
00:20:45,420 --> 00:20:46,550
I'll help you close the door.

339
00:20:46,550 --> 00:20:47,190
Thank you.

340
00:20:53,850 --> 00:20:55,270
Fang Muyang, seriously.

341
00:20:55,293 --> 00:20:57,350
You're causing me trouble
even if you're lying here.

342
00:21:08,390 --> 00:21:09,090
Fei Ni!

343
00:21:09,500 --> 00:21:10,050
Fei Ni!

344
00:21:11,200 --> 00:21:12,480
Fei Ni!

345
00:21:12,871 --> 00:21:15,490
The shortlist of the factory's
recommended university candidates

346
00:21:15,493 --> 00:21:16,220
is announced!

347
00:21:16,390 --> 00:21:17,580
Go and take a look!

348
00:21:32,940 --> 00:21:36,204
(University shortlisted candidates)

349
00:21:36,226 --> 00:21:39,740
(Chen Guodong,
Zhang Xiangyang, Wang Defa)

350
00:21:42,700 --> 00:21:44,620
(Study)

351
00:21:45,404 --> 00:21:46,740
Is everything ready over there?

352
00:21:46,740 --> 00:21:47,937
Everything's ready, Ms. Xu.

353
00:21:48,090 --> 00:21:51,180
Ms. Xu, isn't it still early until the
beginning of the university semester?

354
00:21:51,180 --> 00:21:52,940
Why is the name list released so soon?

355
00:21:52,940 --> 00:21:54,420
Isn't it too early?

356
00:21:54,420 --> 00:21:56,090
I also thought it was too early.

357
00:21:56,090 --> 00:21:58,130
However, Feng Lin was right.

358
00:21:58,130 --> 00:22:01,050
It's better to make a decision
on something so important earlier.

359
00:22:01,050 --> 00:22:03,260
I haven't completed the assessment yet.

360
00:22:05,090 --> 00:22:05,850
What do you mean?

361
00:22:07,740 --> 00:22:09,660
I mean...

362
00:22:10,530 --> 00:22:12,940
I've been taking care of Fang Muyang,

363
00:22:12,940 --> 00:22:15,090
so I didn't pay attention
to the factory...

364
00:22:15,090 --> 00:22:15,980
Fei,

365
00:22:15,980 --> 00:22:17,660
this is the right thing to do.

366
00:22:18,850 --> 00:22:20,570
Your most important task right now

367
00:22:20,570 --> 00:22:22,940
is to take good care of Fang Muyang.

368
00:22:24,050 --> 00:22:24,980
Don't worry.

369
00:22:25,182 --> 00:22:27,360
You'll surely get your chance
in the future.

370
00:22:27,537 --> 00:22:28,460
You understand, right?

371
00:22:59,850 --> 00:23:00,610
Fang Muyang,

372
00:23:03,090 --> 00:23:05,660
do you understand
why I must attend university?

373
00:23:11,180 --> 00:23:12,090
I'm sure you can't.

374
00:23:13,770 --> 00:23:16,090
Not even my parents can understand.

375
00:23:18,660 --> 00:23:20,700
They've been factory workers forever.

376
00:23:22,760 --> 00:23:25,360
They think there's nothing wrong
with being a factory worker.

377
00:23:31,290 --> 00:23:32,180
My brother

378
00:23:33,050 --> 00:23:34,220
and Lin Mei

379
00:23:34,648 --> 00:23:35,900
can't understand as well.

380
00:23:38,050 --> 00:23:39,420
They think

381
00:23:40,740 --> 00:23:43,740
there's no difference between
going to university and being a worker.

382
00:23:45,850 --> 00:23:46,700
But I know...

383
00:23:52,220 --> 00:23:52,980
It's different.

384
00:23:55,220 --> 00:23:56,760
I like to read books.

385
00:23:57,830 --> 00:23:59,330
I like to write.

386
00:24:00,420 --> 00:24:03,050
But I know I'm still incapable.

387
00:24:03,660 --> 00:24:05,330
That is why I want to attend university.

388
00:24:05,330 --> 00:24:07,940
I want to read more books.
I want to learn how to write.

389
00:24:07,940 --> 00:24:10,570
I want to become an author
like Shakespeare.

390
00:24:19,290 --> 00:24:20,500
I dare not

391
00:24:21,460 --> 00:24:23,210
say these things to other people.

392
00:24:24,330 --> 00:24:26,490
They will surely think
that I've gone mad.

393
00:24:32,626 --> 00:24:34,050
In order to attend university,

394
00:24:34,050 --> 00:24:36,260
I'm willing to go through
all kinds of suffering.

395
00:24:36,260 --> 00:24:38,740
However, they just wouldn't let me go.

396
00:24:40,940 --> 00:24:42,790
I just don't get it.

397
00:24:43,020 --> 00:24:45,550
Why do people like Feng Lin,
who doesn't even know the term

398
00:24:45,550 --> 00:24:46,940
that means pure and clear,

399
00:24:46,940 --> 00:24:48,090
can attend university,

400
00:24:48,090 --> 00:24:48,970
but I can't

401
00:24:49,660 --> 00:24:51,870
even get a recommendation spot?

402
00:24:54,050 --> 00:24:55,700
I didn't even dare to say that.

403
00:24:58,180 --> 00:25:01,420
Because Ms. Xu might say
that I'm not being humble.

404
00:25:02,130 --> 00:25:02,920
But

405
00:25:04,260 --> 00:25:06,540
can I attend university
just by being humble?

406
00:25:16,290 --> 00:25:18,380
If the college entrance examination
still exists,

407
00:25:18,720 --> 00:25:20,230
I'll surely qualify for it,

408
00:25:20,610 --> 00:25:22,110
but it no longer exists

409
00:25:22,800 --> 00:25:25,270
so I can't decide my own fate.

410
00:25:26,520 --> 00:25:29,800
Fang Muyang, I'm not greedy at all.

411
00:25:30,330 --> 00:25:31,020
I just

412
00:25:31,020 --> 00:25:31,610
don't want

413
00:25:31,610 --> 00:25:34,315
to live every day of my life
knowing what will happen at the end.

414
00:25:35,940 --> 00:25:37,250
I beg you.

415
00:25:40,050 --> 00:25:41,248
Wake up.

416
00:26:07,500 --> 00:26:08,680
Why are you crying?

417
00:26:19,130 --> 00:26:20,130
Fang Muyang,

418
00:26:23,250 --> 00:26:24,090
you're awake.

419
00:26:25,090 --> 00:26:25,880
Fang Muyang.

420
00:26:28,420 --> 00:26:29,570
Who are you?

421
00:26:32,500 --> 00:26:33,530
I am Fei Ni.

422
00:26:37,130 --> 00:26:37,980
Fei Ni.

423
00:26:39,900 --> 00:26:40,700
Fei Ni.

424
00:26:48,180 --> 00:26:49,020
Fei Ni.

425
00:26:50,380 --> 00:26:53,780
(Inpatient Department)

426
00:26:59,090 --> 00:27:00,220
We will only know

427
00:27:00,220 --> 00:27:02,570
the detailed results
after his brain scan is completed.

428
00:27:02,740 --> 00:27:04,700
However, from his reaction,

429
00:27:04,700 --> 00:27:05,740
the blood clot in the brain

430
00:27:05,740 --> 00:27:07,160
seems to be absorbing quite well.

431
00:27:07,160 --> 00:27:08,370
Moreover, his motor functions

432
00:27:08,370 --> 00:27:09,382
seem to be working well.

433
00:27:09,382 --> 00:27:10,850
Thank you, Dr. Liang.

434
00:27:11,260 --> 00:27:12,290
Fang Muyang,

435
00:27:12,330 --> 00:27:13,700
while you were in a coma,

436
00:27:13,700 --> 00:27:15,420
Fei Ni had been
the one taking care of you.

437
00:27:15,570 --> 00:27:17,050
It's all thanks to her

438
00:27:17,050 --> 00:27:18,293
that you can wake up so soon.

439
00:27:18,330 --> 00:27:20,130
- Yes.
- You need to thank her well.

440
00:27:20,982 --> 00:27:21,950
What is this place?

441
00:27:23,260 --> 00:27:23,610
This...

442
00:27:24,420 --> 00:27:26,500
This is the hospital.

443
00:27:27,090 --> 00:27:29,050
You saved someone
and got injured because of it.

444
00:27:29,420 --> 00:27:30,590
Don't you remember?

445
00:27:32,700 --> 00:27:35,050
Do you still remember what your name is

446
00:27:35,071 --> 00:27:36,382
and where you come from?

447
00:27:52,180 --> 00:27:55,740
(Jiangcheng Worker-Peasant Hospital)

448
00:27:57,330 --> 00:27:58,260
Fang Muyang,

449
00:27:58,900 --> 00:28:02,090
not only are you a morally noble person,

450
00:28:02,530 --> 00:28:04,610
but you are also a resolute person.

451
00:28:04,610 --> 00:28:06,248
All of Jiangcheng No. 1 Textile Factory

452
00:28:06,315 --> 00:28:08,500
are happy to see you out of the coma.

453
00:28:08,500 --> 00:28:09,770
Does he not remember anything,

454
00:28:09,770 --> 00:28:10,740
including his name,

455
00:28:10,740 --> 00:28:11,460
where he lives,

456
00:28:11,537 --> 00:28:12,620
and who his parents are?

457
00:28:14,130 --> 00:28:15,090
Dr. Liang says

458
00:28:15,090 --> 00:28:17,290
he is suffering from retrograde amnesia

459
00:28:17,290 --> 00:28:19,980
resulting from a moderate
closed traumatic brain injury.

460
00:28:20,420 --> 00:28:21,330
It means

461
00:28:21,330 --> 00:28:23,940
he has forgotten
his basic living capabilities.

462
00:28:24,090 --> 00:28:25,940
Doesn't that mean
he has turned into an idiot?

463
00:28:27,500 --> 00:28:29,530
Such a handsome idiot. What a pity.

464
00:28:29,850 --> 00:28:32,260
How is he an idiot?

465
00:28:32,260 --> 00:28:35,330
Dr. Liang said

466
00:28:35,420 --> 00:28:36,940
he needs time

467
00:28:37,260 --> 00:28:38,260
to recover slowly.

468
00:28:38,260 --> 00:28:39,050
For how long?

469
00:28:39,260 --> 00:28:40,740
I don't know.

470
00:28:42,026 --> 00:28:43,493
It's the same as saying nothing.

471
00:28:47,090 --> 00:28:47,840
Hold on.

472
00:28:48,610 --> 00:28:49,740
Does it mean he has forgotten

473
00:28:49,740 --> 00:28:51,080
about you taking care of him?

474
00:28:51,270 --> 00:28:52,560
You've lost out on so much, then.

475
00:28:54,050 --> 00:28:55,820
I just need Ms. Xu to remember.

476
00:29:01,610 --> 00:29:02,740
Fang Muyang,

477
00:29:03,660 --> 00:29:04,720
do you still remember me?

478
00:29:08,210 --> 00:29:08,970
Fei Ni?

479
00:29:09,700 --> 00:29:10,940
I am not Fei Ni.

480
00:29:11,670 --> 00:29:13,080
You saved me.

481
00:29:14,370 --> 00:29:15,340
Do you not remember?

482
00:29:20,130 --> 00:29:21,260
It's fine.

483
00:29:22,020 --> 00:29:23,130
Fang Muyang,

484
00:29:24,220 --> 00:29:26,330
I contacted your mill.

485
00:29:26,660 --> 00:29:28,940
You are a model individual over there.

486
00:29:28,940 --> 00:29:30,740
An example that everyone can learn from.

487
00:29:30,740 --> 00:29:33,810
If you have any problems in the future,

488
00:29:34,130 --> 00:29:35,420
you can come to me.

489
00:29:37,370 --> 00:29:37,900
Fei Ni.

490
00:29:39,660 --> 00:29:40,610
Of course.

491
00:29:41,490 --> 00:29:42,970
Fei Ni, as well.

492
00:29:43,740 --> 00:29:44,810
Fei Ni,

493
00:29:44,980 --> 00:29:46,700
you've worked hard.

494
00:29:46,850 --> 00:29:47,770
Fang Muyang

495
00:29:47,770 --> 00:29:49,700
kept mentioning your name just now.

496
00:29:49,700 --> 00:29:52,360
It's obvious that you've spent
a lot of effort during this period.

497
00:29:52,850 --> 00:29:54,180
Not at all, Ms. Xu.

498
00:29:54,810 --> 00:29:56,020
I've decided

499
00:29:56,020 --> 00:29:57,530
to get someone

500
00:29:57,660 --> 00:29:59,180
to write both of your stories

501
00:29:59,180 --> 00:30:00,330
after he recovers completely.

502
00:30:00,850 --> 00:30:03,660
I will report it
in front of every employee

503
00:30:03,660 --> 00:30:05,248
before making a report to the superior.

504
00:30:05,420 --> 00:30:06,300
I also want to call

505
00:30:06,500 --> 00:30:08,560
every worker
from every industry and system

506
00:30:08,900 --> 00:30:10,160
to learn from both of you.

507
00:30:10,980 --> 00:30:13,600
When the time comes,
not only the role model in the factory,

508
00:30:14,500 --> 00:30:16,080
but I'll also recommend you

509
00:30:16,080 --> 00:30:17,630
to become the whole city's role model.

510
00:30:18,330 --> 00:30:20,330
Ms. Xu, there's no need.

511
00:30:20,330 --> 00:30:21,900
I understand.

512
00:30:22,330 --> 00:30:24,050
Taking care of a patient like this

513
00:30:24,050 --> 00:30:25,810
is hard work.

514
00:30:25,980 --> 00:30:26,700
Don't worry.

515
00:30:27,130 --> 00:30:29,330
I can see the effort you've put in.

516
00:30:29,900 --> 00:30:31,510
The factory's superior sees it too.

517
00:30:32,180 --> 00:30:34,090
When you become the city's role model,

518
00:30:34,182 --> 00:30:36,160
you'll be able
to attend any university you want.

519
00:30:38,220 --> 00:30:38,900
Really?

520
00:30:41,137 --> 00:30:42,980
Thank you for
your recognition, Ms. Xu.

521
00:30:43,330 --> 00:30:47,940
Of course, he must
make a full recovery first.

522
00:30:49,460 --> 00:30:50,810
Don't worry, Ms. Xu.

523
00:30:50,810 --> 00:30:52,700
I will never give up halfway.

524
00:30:52,740 --> 00:30:54,660
I will surely
take good care of Fang Muyang

525
00:30:54,660 --> 00:30:56,570
and see that he makes a full recovery.

526
00:30:57,260 --> 00:31:00,090
Then, I'll leave him to you.

527
00:31:00,660 --> 00:31:01,530
Don't worry.

528
00:31:07,330 --> 00:31:09,330
What did Ms. Xu mean?

529
00:31:10,610 --> 00:31:12,130
She means

530
00:31:12,660 --> 00:31:14,810
if Fang Muyang
can have his memory restored,

531
00:31:14,850 --> 00:31:17,810
I will have a chance
to attend university!

532
00:31:29,740 --> 00:31:31,200
You drew this whole book.

533
00:31:31,460 --> 00:31:32,360
Take a good look.

534
00:31:32,626 --> 00:31:33,850
Stop adjusting the dial.

535
00:31:36,410 --> 00:31:38,770
Look at this. A lumber mill.

536
00:31:39,460 --> 00:31:39,850
Look.

537
00:31:42,940 --> 00:31:44,330
Look at this crane.

538
00:31:44,330 --> 00:31:45,471
I'm sure you remember this.

539
00:31:45,493 --> 00:31:46,180
I don't.

540
00:31:47,570 --> 00:31:48,420
This.

541
00:31:48,420 --> 00:31:50,260
Is this Ling Yi? Take a good look.

542
00:31:50,610 --> 00:31:51,500
I don't know.

543
00:31:52,260 --> 00:31:53,530
Ling Yi.

544
00:31:53,530 --> 00:31:54,330
Right?

545
00:31:54,330 --> 00:31:55,260
Take a good look.

546
00:31:56,660 --> 00:31:57,500
This...

547
00:31:58,290 --> 00:31:59,090
Take a look.

548
00:32:00,090 --> 00:32:01,471
Do you remember them?

549
00:32:01,850 --> 00:32:02,990
They are your colleagues.

550
00:32:03,940 --> 00:32:05,080
Can you remember?

551
00:32:05,530 --> 00:32:07,260
I don't remember. I don't know.

552
00:32:15,660 --> 00:32:16,250
Eat this.

553
00:32:16,500 --> 00:32:18,400
The doctor says
it's good for your brain.

554
00:32:30,810 --> 00:32:31,660
Fang Muyang,

555
00:32:31,660 --> 00:32:33,610
why do you always look at the watch?

556
00:32:34,420 --> 00:32:36,660
Does it mean something special?

557
00:32:40,770 --> 00:32:42,740
Was it given to you by your parents

558
00:32:42,900 --> 00:32:44,570
or your grandmother?

559
00:32:55,180 --> 00:32:55,790
Keep eating.

560
00:33:02,537 --> 00:33:04,582
Two sticks a day.
One in the morning, one at night.

561
00:33:15,360 --> 00:33:16,650
Do you still remember this?

562
00:33:17,330 --> 00:33:18,630
You sold it to me for 1.5 yuan

563
00:33:19,290 --> 00:33:20,820
at the canola field.

564
00:33:21,610 --> 00:33:22,660
Open it.

565
00:33:27,030 --> 00:33:28,250
A book by Shakespeare.

566
00:33:28,660 --> 00:33:31,430
You could even recite his "Sonnet 14".

567
00:33:38,330 --> 00:33:39,940
Didn't you learn how to draw?

568
00:33:39,940 --> 00:33:43,020
You collected all these
famous paintings from around the world.

569
00:34:14,730 --> 00:34:16,800
It's good for restoring your memory.

570
00:34:20,710 --> 00:34:21,330
Eat.

571
00:34:29,300 --> 00:34:30,430
Take a big bite.

572
00:34:46,170 --> 00:34:47,780
Help!

573
00:34:47,980 --> 00:34:49,610
The house is collapsing!

574
00:34:56,610 --> 00:34:59,460
Ms. Liu, who saved you?

575
00:34:59,460 --> 00:35:03,170
It's that young man. Thank you.

576
00:35:07,690 --> 00:35:08,820
It's all right.

577
00:35:08,820 --> 00:35:10,500
Everyone, wake everyone up!

578
00:35:10,500 --> 00:35:11,980
Stop sleeping!

579
00:35:11,980 --> 00:35:14,340
It will collapse again!

580
00:35:14,860 --> 00:35:17,460
Wake everyone up! Stop sleeping!

581
00:35:18,200 --> 00:35:20,030
Mom, I'm scared.

582
00:35:20,940 --> 00:35:22,230
What should we do?

583
00:35:22,530 --> 00:35:25,170
The tree is going to fall on the house!

584
00:35:26,340 --> 00:35:29,530
Who is it? It's still that young man!

585
00:35:29,530 --> 00:35:32,500
He has already saved four people.

586
00:35:32,500 --> 00:35:34,980
Four people!

587
00:35:38,460 --> 00:35:39,570
Do you remember?

588
00:35:43,690 --> 00:35:44,610
Fang Muyang,

589
00:35:47,170 --> 00:35:48,900
I've been waiting for this weather

590
00:35:48,900 --> 00:35:50,650
for half a month.

591
00:35:50,650 --> 00:35:52,650
I heard my father say

592
00:35:52,650 --> 00:35:54,300
the weather was similar that night.

593
00:35:54,300 --> 00:35:55,980
There was a heavy storm.

594
00:35:56,170 --> 00:35:57,980
You saved three people.

595
00:35:57,980 --> 00:35:59,940
Then, the house collapsed

596
00:35:59,940 --> 00:36:00,980
and the tree fell.

597
00:36:00,980 --> 00:36:02,610
You ran inside quickly.

598
00:36:07,090 --> 00:36:08,130
What next?

599
00:36:09,130 --> 00:36:11,500
After that, you were lying here.

600
00:36:15,340 --> 00:36:16,170
I don't remember.

601
00:36:21,650 --> 00:36:22,530
It's all right.

602
00:36:23,980 --> 00:36:24,980
I'll keep thinking.

603
00:36:26,340 --> 00:36:27,710
There must be other ways.

604
00:36:39,170 --> 00:36:39,760
Fei Ni.

605
00:36:42,980 --> 00:36:44,137
I will work hard.

606
00:36:53,780 --> 00:36:54,860
That's good enough.

607
00:37:01,260 --> 00:37:04,980
(Jiangcheng Worker-Peasant Hospital)

608
00:37:12,460 --> 00:37:13,490
What is he doing?

609
00:37:14,050 --> 00:37:14,890
Playing the piano.

610
00:37:15,050 --> 00:37:16,404
He has been playing it for days.

611
00:37:17,050 --> 00:37:17,870
Playing the piano?

612
00:37:18,980 --> 00:37:20,420
You are an expert in piano.

613
00:37:20,420 --> 00:37:21,780
Go and teach him.

614
00:37:22,090 --> 00:37:23,300
Stop teasing me.

615
00:37:26,020 --> 00:37:27,120
How has he been recently?

616
00:37:27,137 --> 00:37:28,620
Has his memory recovered a little?

617
00:37:31,693 --> 00:37:33,070
Are you sure you want to do this?

618
00:37:33,780 --> 00:37:34,890
Taking care of an idiot

619
00:37:35,170 --> 00:37:37,200
is harder than taking care
of a patient in a coma.

620
00:37:37,610 --> 00:37:38,570
I'll say it again.

621
00:37:38,570 --> 00:37:41,200
He's not an idiot.
He just forgets things.

622
00:37:42,380 --> 00:37:43,230
You are right.

623
00:37:43,690 --> 00:37:44,490
He is not an idiot.

624
00:37:44,940 --> 00:37:45,950
You are the idiot.

625
00:37:47,500 --> 00:37:48,100
Fei Ni,

626
00:37:48,690 --> 00:37:49,960
you must listen to me this time.

627
00:37:50,380 --> 00:37:52,310
This is a trap.
Stop sinking deeper into it.

628
00:37:54,380 --> 00:37:56,160
Ms. Xu said

629
00:37:57,090 --> 00:37:58,860
that if I can take good care of him,

630
00:37:58,990 --> 00:38:00,782
she will recommend me
to attend university.

631
00:38:00,930 --> 00:38:02,450
I can't just give up so easily.

632
00:38:02,980 --> 00:38:04,170
What if he can't recover?

633
00:38:04,820 --> 00:38:05,280
Well,

634
00:38:05,980 --> 00:38:07,650
people also said he couldn't wake up

635
00:38:07,650 --> 00:38:09,210
but he still woke up.

636
00:38:12,090 --> 00:38:15,370
Fei Ni, if you can't do it this year,
there's always next year.

637
00:38:15,380 --> 00:38:17,730
If you can't do it next year,
there's always the year after next.

638
00:38:17,737 --> 00:38:19,826
This is not the only way
to attend university.

639
00:38:23,720 --> 00:38:24,780
Lin Mei,

640
00:38:25,530 --> 00:38:26,670
you know. I...

641
00:38:27,500 --> 00:38:29,160
I've been working hard for three years.

642
00:38:30,050 --> 00:38:31,540
I know very well

643
00:38:32,020 --> 00:38:33,310
that every failure

644
00:38:33,460 --> 00:38:35,300
makes me less determined.

645
00:38:35,780 --> 00:38:38,650
I don't know if I still have the courage
to fight for it next year.

646
00:38:39,250 --> 00:38:41,210
I don't want to see my determination

647
00:38:41,380 --> 00:38:42,860
being worn away little by little.

648
00:38:45,004 --> 00:38:46,448
Do you think I don't know you?

649
00:38:47,250 --> 00:38:47,980
You will

650
00:38:48,570 --> 00:38:50,240
only give up when you hit a wall.

651
00:38:50,980 --> 00:38:51,520
No.

652
00:38:51,560 --> 00:38:53,210
You won't give up
even if you hit a wall.

653
00:38:56,050 --> 00:38:58,000
Who knows
when he will regain his memory?

654
00:39:00,090 --> 00:39:00,740
Oh,

655
00:39:01,210 --> 00:39:03,570
doesn't he have
any relatives or friends?

656
00:39:07,420 --> 00:39:09,250
He does have one.

657
00:39:10,050 --> 00:39:12,740
Perhaps it might work if she's here.

658
00:39:17,020 --> 00:39:17,780
Where is he?

659
00:39:18,500 --> 00:39:19,030
Fei Ni.

660
00:39:25,210 --> 00:39:26,170
You're still smiling?

661
00:39:26,190 --> 00:39:28,570
You're an adult, but you can't even
tie your own shoelaces.

662
00:39:28,570 --> 00:39:29,226
Come here.

663
00:39:35,090 --> 00:39:36,190
Just leave it here.

664
00:39:37,570 --> 00:39:38,080
Squat down.

665
00:39:40,020 --> 00:39:42,090
It might be hard,
but you still need to learn it.

666
00:39:42,750 --> 00:39:43,630
Tie a knot.

667
00:39:44,780 --> 00:39:45,640
Make it into a circle.

668
00:39:46,404 --> 00:39:48,648
Why are you looking at me?
Look at your shoes.

669
00:39:51,020 --> 00:39:51,650
Turn it around.

670
00:39:52,020 --> 00:39:52,860
Tie it tightly.

671
00:39:53,860 --> 00:39:54,830
He might be a fool,

672
00:39:54,848 --> 00:39:56,360
but he's easy to take care of.

673
00:40:10,690 --> 00:40:11,500
Fang Muyang.

674
00:40:22,690 --> 00:40:23,820
You're here.

675
00:40:27,820 --> 00:40:28,900
Ling Yi.

676
00:40:29,780 --> 00:40:31,090
She's here to see you.

677
00:40:31,090 --> 00:40:32,780
Quick. Take a good look at her.

678
00:40:33,050 --> 00:40:34,650
Can you remember anything?

679
00:40:35,210 --> 00:40:36,020
Fang Muyang,

680
00:40:36,570 --> 00:40:38,090
have you really forgotten about me?

681
00:40:38,420 --> 00:40:40,070
I am Ling Yi...

682
00:40:46,380 --> 00:40:47,648
Stop wasting your energy.

683
00:40:48,170 --> 00:40:49,430
He doesn't even remember me.

684
00:40:49,430 --> 00:40:50,340
(Fang Mujing)

685
00:40:51,550 --> 00:40:53,120
Jing, you're here too.

686
00:40:58,570 --> 00:40:59,780
You must be Fei Ni.

687
00:41:02,170 --> 00:41:03,500
Hello, I am Fang Mujing.

688
00:41:03,980 --> 00:41:05,080
I am Fang Muyang's sister.

689
00:41:08,800 --> 00:41:09,540
Hello, Mujing.

690
00:41:26,680 --> 00:41:27,360
Fei Ni.

691
00:41:27,715 --> 00:41:29,737
Thank you
for taking care of Fang Muyang.

692
00:41:30,730 --> 00:41:31,780
You don't have to thank me.

693
00:41:31,804 --> 00:41:34,840
Taking care of him is a task given to me
by Jiangcheng No. 1 Textile Factory.

694
00:41:37,470 --> 00:41:38,830
Thank you for still visiting him.

695
00:41:39,500 --> 00:41:41,990
Jing, you don't need
to be so polite to me.

696
00:41:44,500 --> 00:41:45,740
I had a chat with Dr. Liang.

697
00:41:46,250 --> 00:41:47,440
Right now, Fang Muyang

698
00:41:47,690 --> 00:41:49,320
lacks the ability to live on his own.

699
00:41:49,820 --> 00:41:50,860
Most importantly,

700
00:41:51,300 --> 00:41:53,220
no one knows when he will recover

701
00:41:53,226 --> 00:41:54,826
or whether he will even recover.

702
00:41:54,826 --> 00:41:56,582
He needs someone to take care of him.

703
00:41:56,760 --> 00:41:58,089
However, in Jiangcheng,

704
00:41:58,090 --> 00:42:00,204
there's no one in my family
who can take care of him.

705
00:42:00,690 --> 00:42:01,540
So, I've decided

706
00:42:02,090 --> 00:42:02,740
to send him

707
00:42:02,900 --> 00:42:05,010
to a rehabilitation center
in my hometown tomorrow.

708
00:42:09,920 --> 00:42:10,880
Why?

709
00:42:11,050 --> 00:42:12,210
I can take care of him.

710
00:42:12,210 --> 00:42:13,510
How long can you do that for?

711
00:42:14,610 --> 00:42:15,460
A month?

712
00:42:15,460 --> 00:42:16,370
Two months?

713
00:42:16,820 --> 00:42:18,000
Or half a year to a year?

714
00:42:18,380 --> 00:42:20,460
If he can't recover
in three to five years,

715
00:42:20,670 --> 00:42:22,190
can you take care of him forever?

716
00:42:25,680 --> 00:42:28,650
But the rehabilitation center
in the hometown isn't good enough.

717
00:42:28,650 --> 00:42:29,520
That's a given.

718
00:42:32,420 --> 00:42:33,440
But if he stays here,

719
00:42:33,890 --> 00:42:36,210
the No. 1 Textile Factory
or Educated Youth Office

720
00:42:36,570 --> 00:42:37,830
won't keep taking care of him.

721
00:42:39,020 --> 00:42:39,700
Or

722
00:42:41,300 --> 00:42:43,200
can you take care of him
in my place forever?

723
00:42:45,404 --> 00:42:46,170
Speaking of which,

724
00:42:46,170 --> 00:42:48,420
if he hadn't given you
his university quota,

725
00:42:48,420 --> 00:42:50,071
he might not even get hurt.

726
00:42:51,420 --> 00:42:53,920
Just think of it as repaying him.
Can you do that?

727
00:43:01,370 --> 00:43:02,820
If you can't keep taking care of him

728
00:43:02,820 --> 00:43:04,410
until he recovers,

729
00:43:05,250 --> 00:43:06,510
I'll make the decision.

730
00:43:07,004 --> 00:43:08,400
I only applied for four days off.

731
00:43:08,410 --> 00:43:10,290
I'll leave on the morning
of the day after tomorrow.

732
00:43:10,300 --> 00:43:13,020
Tomorrow, I'll come here
and process his discharge.

733
00:43:28,860 --> 00:43:33,340
♪After the laughter, I think of you♪

734
00:43:35,900 --> 00:43:40,620
♪After the storm, I think of you♪

735
00:43:43,140 --> 00:43:49,260
♪In the little courtyard,
there you are dancing♪

736
00:43:50,260 --> 00:43:54,820
♪That earnest you,
smiling so innocently♪

737
00:43:57,300 --> 00:44:02,060
♪In spring, I stay by your side♪

738
00:44:04,500 --> 00:44:08,860
♪When summer comes, I watch over you♪

739
00:44:11,220 --> 00:44:17,860
♪In the light of dawn, you belong to me♪

740
00:44:17,860 --> 00:44:27,460
♪At the edge of the world,
I will still hold you tight♪

741
00:44:28,540 --> 00:44:34,700
♪There is a small place♪

742
00:44:34,700 --> 00:44:41,500
♪Where they carry big dreams♪

743
00:44:41,500 --> 00:44:48,860
♪Every lovely face♪

744
00:44:49,740 --> 00:44:55,900
♪Shines brightly in the heart♪

745
00:44:56,700 --> 00:45:02,740
♪Even when we collide,
we hold our course♪

746
00:45:03,940 --> 00:45:09,740
♪Even when we stumble,
we keep our resolve♪

747
00:45:10,820 --> 00:45:17,100
♪My you, walking toward the distance♪

748
00:45:17,900 --> 00:45:26,140
♪Please carry our dreams
and let them soar♪
